WHO   — Brandi Svenning — the prize she never agreed to be
WHAT  — The reluctant center of the spectacle: a person turned into a game-show prize by the people who claim to love her.
WHERE — MLR · Mallrats (1995)  Framework inputs: Mallrats (1995, dir. Kevin Smith, Gramercy/View Askew); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film's satire of the dating show needs its unwilling star.
HOW   — By being volunteered for a televised romance while the boy she actually wants storms the set.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  My dad put my love life on television. I never agreed to be the prize — I just want to choose for myself.

